results.name: Expansion of the polynomial x^12*(x^6-1)*(x^4-1)*(x^3-1)*(x-1) in increasing powers of x.
comment: q^24*(q^12-1)*(q^8-1)*(q^6-1)*(q^2-1) is the order of the simple group F_4(q), if q is a prime power.
reference: R. L. Griess, Jr., Twelve Sporadic Groups, Springer, 1998; see p. 169.
results.author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Dec 26 2010
